        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This division covers built environment and design.
It includes:
• architecture;
• building;
• design; and
• urban and regional planning.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Indigenous built environment and design is included in Division 45 Indigenous studies.</skos:scopeNote>
