    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers design.
It includes:
• design history and theory;
• ergonomics;
• industrial design;
• textile and fashion design; and
• visual communication and graphics design.</skos:definition>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Architectural design and architectural history is included in Group 3301 Architecture.
b) Engineering design is included in Group 4010 Engineering practice and education.
c) Fine arts are included in Group 3606 Visual Arts.</skos:scopeNote>
