    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers medicinal and biomolecular chemistry.
It includes cheminformatics.</skos:definition>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Biochemistry other than medical biochemistry or biomolecular chemistry is included in Group 3101 Biochemistry and cell biology.
b) Pharmacology for animal use is included in Group 3009 Veterinary sciences.
c) Food chemistry is included in Group 3006 Food sciences.
d) Medical biochemistry is included in Group 3205 Medical biochemistry and metabolomics.
e) Clinical chemistry is included in Group 3202 Clinical sciences.
f) Pharmacology for human use and human toxicology is included in Group 3214 Pharmacology and pharmaceutical sciences.</skos:scopeNote>
