        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers business systems in context.</skos:definition>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Data models, systems and quality are included in Group 4605 Data management and data science.
b) Information modelling, management and ontologies are included in Group 4609 Information systems.
