    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">This group covers applied ethics. It included human rights and justice issues.</skos:definition>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">a) Humane treatment of animals in agriculture, domestic or sporting environments is included in Group 3003 Animal production.
